FBIS4-20282 "drweu083_p_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-083 Daily Report 28 Apr 1994 GREECE Spokesman Comments on Turkish Statement on Cyprus Spokesman Comments on Turkish Statement on Cyprus NC2804182894 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1130 GMT 28 Apr 94 NC2804182894 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] Government spokesman Evangelos Venizelos said the joint statement of the Turkish National Assembly parties expresses the well-known, classic, intransigent Turkish positions on the Cyprus issue. He added: This is not an encouraging indication and it has been recorded by the United Nations and the United States, which have expressed a positive view toward a Cyprus solution.
